        <b>Key Strategies for Water Conservation</b>
    </div>
    <ul>
        <li><div class="alldiv">
            <b>Efficient Water Use:</b> Avoid wastage by turning off taps when not in use, fixing leaks promptly, and using water-saving appliances and fixtures like low-flow showerheads and dual-flush toilets.
        </div></li>
        <li>
            <div class="alldiv">
                <b>Rainwater Harvesting:</b>Collect and store rainwater for various uses, reducing dependency on groundwater and municipal supplies, and helping recharge aquifers.
            </div>
        </li>
        <li>
            <div class="alldiv">
                <b>Sustainable Irrigation Practices:</b> Adopt efficient irrigation methods such as drip irrigation or sprinkler systems to minimize water loss in agriculture, which is a major consumer of freshwater.
            </div>
        </li>
        <li>
            <div class="alldiv">
                <b>Protection of Water Bodies:</b> Prevent pollution and contamination of rivers, lakes, and groundwater by managing industrial discharge, agricultural runoff, and waste disposal effectively.
            </div>
        </li>
    </ul>
    <div class="hading">
        <b>Water Policy in India: Key Points</b>
    </div>
    <div class="policy">
        <ul>
            <div class="pol">            
                <li><b>Water as a National Resource</b>
                <ul>
                    <li>Water is treated as a common good for equitable distribution.</li>
                    <li>Ensures access to safe and clean drinking water for all.</li>
                </ul>
                </li>
            </div>
            <div class="pol">
                <li><b>Integrated Water Resources Management (IWRM)</b>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Promotes sustainability, conservation, and equitable water use.</li>
                        <li>Integrates water supply, demand, and wastewater management.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </div>

            <div class="pol">
                <li><b>River Basin Management</b>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Encourages planning and management at the river basin level.</li>
                        <li>Advocates forming River Basin Organizations (RBOs).</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </div>
            <div class="pol">
                <li>
                    <b>Water Conservation</b>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Promotes technologies like drip irrigation and water-saving agricultural practices.</li>
                        <li>Emphasizes rainwater harvesting, watershed management, and efficient water use.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </div>

        </ul>
    </div>

